snippet.title: Trailer of Crossing Void - Global Version
snippet.description:
📣Crossing Void - Global is Officially Released!
⬇Click here to download for FREE!!⬇
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1473109438
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.actgames.fcigl
——————————————————————————————————————————————
Welcome to Crossing Void - Global, an amazing anime crossover JRPG game!
An all-star cast from 25 most-loved anime franchises!
Let’s stand united and fight in the new world!
